---
title: Sweet and Savoury Brie Pizzettes with Red Pepper Jelly
description: Brie and red pepper jelly were born to be best friends! Pita bread acts as a perfect base for red pepper jelly, caramelized onions, peppery arugula, ooey-gooey brie cheese, and toasted rosemary walnuts. It's the perfect ending to a long day!
